Subject: drm/amdgpu: init rlcg_reg_access_ctrl for gfx10
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: f8f96b17f0fa302b246e35773074f39e43add023
